  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "As mentioned in section 3, our method does not rely on any external story corpora.",
    "Suspenseful stories can be generated with our method in a fully zero-shot way from ChatGPT.",
    "We start every ChatGPT dialogue session with \"You are a creative storyteller.\".",
    "When generating anything other than stories (e.g., interim information such as the protagonist's goal and actions), to discourage ChatGPT from generating excessively long responses that are usually not quite useful when serving as inputs to subsequent generation stages, we append \"Use no more than [n] sentences in your answer.\"",
    "(n can be three, four, or five) to the prompt when necessary."
  ],
